## ğŸ“Š Dataset Overview  
The dataset contains telecom customer details, service usage, and churn status.  

- ğŸ“Œ **CustomerID** - Unique customer identifier  
- ğŸ“Œ **Tenure** - Number of months a customer has stayed  
- ğŸ“Œ **MonthlyCharges** - Monthly bill amount  
- ğŸ“Œ **TotalCharges** - Total amount paid by the customer  
- ğŸ“Œ **Contract** - Type of contract (Month-to-Month, One Year, Two Years)  
- ğŸ“Œ **Churn** - Whether the customer left (**Yes/No**)  

